{"tid":1312671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世文]和理非將道德標準無形提高","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:12:33.000Z","uid":8296,"like":130,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c88ff65003d7bdeb4437f36bcdfc0202ec74a2c7","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/397730460342646/posts/2327331840715822?s=100002286188388&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F397730460342646%2Fposts%2F2327331840715822%3Fs%3D100002286188388%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=cfbfe961\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/397730460342646/posts/2327331840715822?s=100002286188388&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n又要講一次子貢贖人的故事：<br />\n<br />\n魯國有一條法律，如果有人能把在國外的魯國奴隸贖出，就能到國庫中報銷贖金。有次孔子弟子子貢贖了個奴隸，回國後卻拒絕收下賠償金。<br />\n<br />\n子貢的行為好像很無私高尚，對嗎？<br />\n<br />\n然而這種行為卻受到孔子批評。<br />\n<br />\n孔子說，賜（子貢名端木賜）啊，你這樣做，魯國人再也不肯贖人了。即使你收下賠償金，亦無損你的善行，你這樣做，就無人肯贖人了。<br />\n<br />\n將道德標準提到無限高，其客觀效果是阻人行善。你的私德很偉大光榮正確，道德光環閃閃發光。<br />\n<br />\n但你的頭上光環，是以犧牲社會整體公德為代價。<br />\n<br />\n對了，就是想講淘大連儂牆那位打不還手的戇男。戇男自稱有泰拳底子、跆拳道黑帶，頂得住。<br />\n<br />\n有武術底子，才更加罪加一等。就算你有武術底子頂得住，咁其他人呢？要效法你直到被打死？將道德標準提到無限高，正是這種表面的高尚底下隱藏的邪惡。<br />\n<br />\n再者，你讓旁人錄下過程放上網令打人者被捕，你其實在幫忙維護警察的形象，增加港共警察的合法性。<br />\n<br />\n長於私德而怯於公德，正是和理非的特性。吊詭的是，當這種私德越被推崇，整個社會卻越是腐敗墮落。<br />\n<br />\n文勝質則史，當社會失去了原始的質樸，就會變得虛浮而文過飾非。在香港，於上層是表現為港共的巧言令色語言偽術，在下層就是標榜自我高尚的和理非。<br />\n<br />\n所以即使孔子贊歎周代「郁郁乎文哉」，還是要融合夏商兩代的餘緒，因為夏人質樸尚忠，商人畏天尚敬，監於二代，勿忘初衷，人心才不會變得虛浮。美國憲法允許人民佩槍，也有這一重意義在。<br />\n<br />\n文質彬彬，然後君子，說的是後天的修養教化與原始的血性相稱，才稱得上是君子。自小被豢養的香港人，對於「血性」二字大概相當陌生了。"},{"pid":"16f5c58cfa993c91e205cb73fbc36460a09c508d","tid":1312671,"uid":279326,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"好多學武既人　其實係用武術<br />\n<br />\n保護佢內心既懦弱<br />\n<br />\n俠以武犯禁　哩五個字　唔係好多人明"},{"pid":"437faa790f6e21c6ac0cafbdc2da44c5940d7471","tid":1312671,"uid":80965,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"市民倒地後舉手投降仍然被警察朝面噴胡椒噴霧<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/522889241876907?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F303668637132303%2Fposts%2F522889241876907%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=8afcb53c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/522889241876907?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n用警棍不斷對沒有反抗嘅瘦弱的少女作出擊打<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/169166456593130/posts/1257595487750216?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169166456593130%2Fposts%2F1257595487750216%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=5a224594\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/169166456593130/posts/1257595487750216?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n記者被警察打傷並拿相機<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2803164013089539?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2803164013089539%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=6439c1ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2803164013089539?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n遊行人士被打到重傷 滿地鮮血<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/623064611149143/posts/2141091966013059?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F623064611149143%2Fposts%2F2141091966013059%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=337fcd50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/623064611149143/posts/2141091966013059?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n被警方迫至後退嘅遊行人士被後方警方用警棍打到頭部流血<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2802948696444404?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2802948696444404%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=0053f7c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2802948696444404?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n3個警員壓住一個遊行人士 傷者身體抽搐 嘴角流血<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2803071113098829?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2803071113098829%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=eb68c624\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2803071113098829?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n一班警員突然衝落行人天橋在沒有警告下出椒和警棍狂毆示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/330920327037381/posts/2136037743192288?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F330920327037381%2Fposts%2F2136037743192288%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7cc97c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/330920327037381/posts/2136037743192288?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n警方用武力拘捕示威者，並多次以「差人做嘢」為理由，拒絕記者拍攝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3074478372579356?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3074478372579356%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=0565b70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3074478372579356?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n追捕16歲示威者令佢差啲跌落天橋 半身懸吊空中<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/522914551874376?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F303668637132303%2Fposts%2F522914551874376%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=a2a9ca97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/522914551874376?s=100002216289676&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n議員勸警察冷靜 一野比人用警棍扑頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2311878618849163?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2311878618849163%3Fs%3D100002216289676%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f2a05c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2311878618849163?s=100002216289676&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n女警突然對途人施放胡椒噴霧 但當時嘅情況係連對峙都稱唔上<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pighead.sun/videos/10157040385186391/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpighead.sun%2Fvideos%2F10157040385186391%2F&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=65b909da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pighead.sun/videos/10157040385186391/</a>"},{"pid":"d99a4de6f81bd04fbee45b05c38e4e4be796175b","tid":1312671,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf684c7874256e69ef6373e28bdc730c5bd8cf25","tid":1312671,"uid":57269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"無人會記得你戰爭用咗幾多子彈、燃燒彈、或者幾賤嘅方式，但死亡人數永遠記起歷史，叫我地唔好再有犧牲。唔好再用肉體去硬接傷害，打游擊，打完就走，咁就建立咗中國，你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098ab340c14254d1af296326c59a1ec76d5c3e24","tid":1312671,"uid":42751,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">再者，你讓旁人錄下過程放上網令打人者被捕，你其實在幫忙維護警察的形象，增加港共警察的合法性。</span><br />\n<br />\n好認同呢句，反正一還手，都係義士俾人拉，打人果件廢老乜事都冇，咁點解仲咁死蠢拍片"},{"pid":"30836ce4c643a9f3e9288b3aa402c5a3fa73f8f8","tid":1312671,"uid":274792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"afa5197005777dfc452960170df942845c301fdf","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"294a0c1ce3eaca09b3c751d6af1a3059815e0cb1","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"推到更多手足睇到"},{"pid":"d7eda5b6c94ba4f1ff1ea2ae96634028fc66d159","tid":1312671,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">14/7 聽日一齊去沙田野餐。\n\n唔理你和理非定勇武派 \n請帶齊裝備保護自己\n另外 聽日好曬 一人一長遮\n-\n警方定性612為暴動 繼續追擊警方濫權\n要求成立獨立調查委員會\n繼續五大訴求\n-\n大家繼續努力</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1a919ebc084311877dca30806804e78b2660650b","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"求大家睇下plz"},{"pid":"c2141f4aad80d9295d4b0901313db160aab29212","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:32:16.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"59a3fabec7f0e1ffe8b6dedfc8870a9c99ad285f","tid":1312671,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:33:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ebc7927f47bbc584fa7d402706e8b594b7e7849","tid":1312671,"uid":8296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:21:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6f185a99312b32102e2dd3da8f48bd7eb43f0d17","tid":1312671,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:22:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb954fe1c9816913967cc8e6e946d84c982f778a","tid":1312671,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:23:43.000Z","msg":"槍響之前：金恩博士與三個邪惡的最後鬥爭<br />\n人們當然知道馬丁路德金恩博士為黑人民權運動奮鬥，知道他著名的演說「我有一個夢」，或者知道他在整整五十年前的1968年被槍殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40soundfury%2F%25E6%25A7%258D%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D-%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%2582%25AA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD-c3dd35a3dcf4&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=b38b7262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4</a><br />\n泛民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.不受傷，不流血。<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=d7314b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a>"},{"pid":"f99b4792b8ccf3d10ef2f3324546836d3322ac5b","tid":1312671,"uid":218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T19:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jPtOk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jPtOk8.jpg&h=c2e4dd83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9093989c143762a233c0389676aca637d6adeadc","tid":1312671,"uid":31762,